perl-timedate: perl-timedate (A Perl module for time and date manipulation)
perl-timedate:
perl-timedate: This module includes a number of smaller modules suited for
perl-timedate: manipulation of time and date strings with Perl. In particular, the
perl-timedate: Date::Format and Date::Parse modules can display and read times and
perl-timedate: dates in various formats, providing a more reliable interface to
perl-timedate: textual representations of points in time.
perl-timedate:
